Dear Officers of <%= @request.organization %>,

This email is to inform you that your <%= @request %> has been completed, but requires further action before it will be considered submitted.

The following people must approve the request before it is considered submitted:

<% @request.users.unfulfilled( Approver.where( :quantity => nil ) ).each do |user| -%>
 * <%= user.name %>
<% end -%>

They may approve the request here <<%= new_polymorphic_url( [ @request, 'approval' ] ) %>>.

<% if @request.basis.submissions_due_at && @request.basis.submissions_due_at > DateTime.now -%>
The next deadline for submissions is <%= @request.basis.submissions_due_at.to_s :us_ordinal %>.
<% end -%>

<% if @request.basis.contact_web -%>
More information is available here <<%= @request.basis.contact_web %>>.
<% end -%>

Sincerely,

<%= @request.basis.contact_name %>

